1. Install the sdk.sh for SoM.
2. Setup your cross-compiling envirionment.
        e.g: source ${SoM-sdk-dir}/environment-setup-aarch64-xilinx-linux
3. Excute the source code compile script.
        bash ./build.sh [build_dir]
   where the build_dir is an optional argument you can pass in to assign the directory the buid output will go to.
   by default, it's ./build
